{"id":"9","jsonrpc":"2.0","result":{"contents":{"kind":"markdown","value":"Declared in: cature.cj  \nPackage info: default  \n\n```cangjie\ninternal let let_variable_1: Int64 = 4\n```\n\n---\n\n3. If there is a local variable in a block, closures capture variables of the same name in the outer scope will report a warning.\n"},"range":{"end":{"character":29,"line":90},"start":{"character":15,"line":90}}}}